Lab -2 SRS (Hostel management system)

The system should be used by the 1) Hostel staff containg - Guard, Cloaning staff and mess staff
                                 2) Warden
                                 3) Students
                                 4) Management
                                   
i) The warden should allot rooms, check the attendance records, maintain the mess, and review the complains and feedbacks.
ii) The management should act on complains, collect fee and send fee reminders to the students.
iii) The Students should pay the fees and maintain the room and make complains as and when needed.
iv) Hostel staff should do their own respective duties.
